e a repo-relative path coming from mixed slash inputs.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n return raw_path.strip().replace(\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\"/\\\").replace(\\\"//\\\", \\\"/\\\").lstrip(\\\"./\\\")\\n``...",
